    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176330/extras/77cfdf4712363f8e5a8597772f1da95b.webp?t=1763120034\" width=110 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">The game starts, main menu appears. You press start, but something is wrong.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> Try clicking again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176330/extras/65bad9ab7d7c25d0773ba7532cf03278.webp?t=1763120034\" width=110 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Use A-D to move, Space to jump.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Mind your cursor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176330/extras/27f58d0e38afc3ec7c429ca767e9ebef.webp?t=1763120034\" width=110 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">The main menu has become the game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Navigate glitched UI elements where buttons are platforms, volume sliders move you around, and menu screens hide devious puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> A short experimental platformer that breaks the fourth wall.</p>",
